// DiagramHistoryPreview
// Side-by-side preview of a historical diagram version vs the current version.
// Provides Revert and Back buttons.

FUNCTION formatTimestamp(ts) -> string
  Returns ts.toLocaleString() (full locale date/time string).

---

FUNCTION DiagramHistoryPreview(historicalContent, currentContent, version, onRevert, onBack) -> JSX  EXPORT
  CALLS: MermaidPreview (MermaidPreview)
  Renders two MermaidPreview panes side by side: historical (left) and
  current (right).
  Header shows the formatted version timestamp.
  "Revert to this version" button calls onRevert(historicalContent).
  "Back" button calls onBack.
